{"tid":758884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【係精神嘅】美人計倫敦金億元騙案　警拘押220萬元林寶","createTime":"2018-07-28T06:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T09:30:53.000Z","uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"db836b5fdcdc11fdcf70856b22f7f2a5653a8fc7","tid":758884,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"美人計倫敦金億元騙案　警拘押220萬元林寶<br />\n<br />\n07月28日(六) 13:45更新 11:45建立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180728/photo/bkn-20180728114540172-0728_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180728134542\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180728%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180728114540172-0728_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180728134542&h=b3ecd1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方扣查一輛林寶堅尼跑車。(警方圖片)<br />\n<br />\n警方商業罪案調查科探員，前日(26日)採取第二波打擊倫敦金騙案拉11人後，於昨日（27日）下午約5時，再在北角渣華道發現一輛與案件有關遭通緝的林寶堅尼超級跑車，經調查後相信該跑車屬本案的犯罪得益，價值約220萬港元，警方已扣押該車輛作財富調查。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件至今共拘46人，警方共接獲162人報案，損失金額約1億港元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180728/mobile/bkn-20180728114540172-0728_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180728%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180728114540172-0728_00822_001.html&d=uBYLp38IdER8mI%2BiaMykeQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=185faa17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180728/mobile/bkn-20180728114540172-0728_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b83a97121ef562bd8160d892fa10ac846a9fc9b6","tid":758884,"uid":119494,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"呢架車精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n幾時拍賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\